HEADWORD: Bewitching
<hw>Be*witch"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having power to bewitch or
fascinate; enchanting; captivating; charming.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Be*witch"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
Be*witch"ing*ness, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

